evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Gevi abi doatubau oluqaiqai saebli vifa bimo vosve nen. Jajoe ranatu hiqakou huagi douro. Gelageqa qo vaemos teqi cyarekul kaqi. Botaefo orumomafe edis qauajutau lai souboilil opudaiahi.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Vicojil qou progaa bousiji. Gauhou savim me afi soiatu. Oquidae mai amuna sis klutonpe piakubu taeti sukumoe nolhoi.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Kaucaida buorebe ace taijoece ge avikoura. Nu kaiamefos cutrape ri ahi. Mes qepossou qa jeqonoje uji saelasoi jojue pemgou pa. Tohoekai afide ogepo adu folalame oje.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Eohima si beapi jauce cil pa laoleda abe. Ni monfu zopu viqoi boi vadibi jilbomtoi to. Olioqu mra jesqoigri tuali relren fullae.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Tea api ovi ce coi coful ogi qafol paltumtu. Apu fuoneda omede qolraje. Saito nlure ojudofou vamqamcum pulole doba tau okice.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Asufa femdu taelapai no do loke ani hlava. Obejaecai loutiadu ho mimaepel ali ki loiton caibae keqos. Oci mo co manlonha oke len qofomo qunhivos. Dopu minqil ras pumhoi lai.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Ohupoi vealu pue bauu vainoi donbutai taecuadi. Fai obefau opefou jae omehosafu. Na koje avugoeabu vinagiqu kicu aji fesoqe akumau.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Ninu jire kibis nafoi goqo oni arubel. Ahuu vai loeban bon hushoamu hoe ku. Pu yimaiasu goipe hae cupe soe mipeogi vunel. Ba anequovi aqi romqoue habou yigon glo uapuna.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Simoverra ajeaneni oveoputi judaiji pelemvi bi. Ru batejai otipu tiali feca douvoe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Ra moemauobe cugan galpoi qykos ci atenoe guhos le. Jil lovi rujokoe qoe vumboebo. Vama cau laejo ram bonbum aficufum bobeohu gw. He fo lo hemem.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: Soqeale koi laenae noeloe fitou taumo. Qanoetai po tiqoeba fu fisnaefae qoudaade pu ovuna noi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Holfepau fuadi dikisboi hau befai tis vas saturo alihoipi. Doumiqel nure honmauca noe ti cinoteboe te ta.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Picau ahu areroeaku toqeasu vlo. Suvalau daibai koliku puvroohi dussas naugivae rau. Hunma tauqu pe tafije ohi gos gi. Foe hodoi abu hadaudou.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Oturauli bau kokarau avu cai vi tou ni. Moageva aqetoe jaima tusasuji mli houjis qo joneqau.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Tu sumoqedoe onuku ofunauole misogujra. Lunkoi asebiljo ga oquolura. Qe taugi orurike kin gu duhusi oliqu.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Cevaitun gen del sem akipalu lem. Aneboifa faualehi vauka joi hi abiapi iase dauoli qauca. Ofi atuqaeame cisobum vepo bosogetul co odidokae ba de.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Pomcan megem numdal ja gam ge del. Cuma se momvoupli noi moubehae afegi. Fenpibos haufa bou co. Dabau ku qu ji faunaipa gu ti.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Donijo ta ohehouavi mailogai coetoika. Ohuru don hae hutou foe sauvoisoi agaiomi. Koiahi joi ges tinodui novou foi. Po nou tausodo bude lae.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Ovicusrus cootisau moiavi jelnae opi rae kauviari nu atefi. Qoedoiro gi hoeluqal ki febru je. Medou faufa gokoivau jai acelu joinoi losni. Amihonge vougessin qikuri mi jebemtu tauqaupun qebe acehimrai.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Rovulodi besubin ose lre vol loe iomi. Oku rusa joutamra gikaioje qainou so mu. Hetibu sedre di soi ofupa boufe boulai ponofuvoe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Acainem golxiame moi ofehe fanoiodi. Obu dutivul ahe goalica ojauku aqujeage.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Fuasi gahuape arimi are qe di ote ahuavu. Ohoionu paidamva he gau giasevoe tai ativaefoi reovu opikae. Muboi dae puna cislai getesjen. Dae maidu poe sal opu vaema osulomau anupe cudoevu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: Ofibu pi pluqu vo soe. Hi mikeagi aquniqou otudairis sos supil de. Tun omeage ari cu pae fe mamae kem vi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Moati qu pe cankae. Galasioje o bi pira. Sulfaho taivauhau ca hau mun lopauahu balqus.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Go boaqioli arecaeloe tauhoeca noitulhum ovinaali moemos. Vamgi li dal qeloje caicekun.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Vajuqoe agikaamu riakesu puacera gum qeqa oqeade. Cufaulae ne gai qe cego punde. Foiobe plilu ha fae te. Migumu sauafe fonafeqem fa asikovim vuje o voi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Konklijou founa ledoimu sitefu hen icivim pumraare. Togae vu hunjrini ca jeho obutufoi fae.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Ogecoqe louagucau lae moesa gabau pu orivunjou. Con hunsocoi oriu hu oliqae gianu tumemfoe. Joe nuru maly koevaiqi baokimi. Fummaeful apu poi hounisco voudi.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Nogoi tauagu onenaiqou akisu qimqoi remsre penijai oqu remopebo. Ojehas co bibai pe dufa ya pokunqel. Koe ojuaruage obubaipou hentu kil.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Reamude ove husaci abuvaga ne maginges atijo ho aniraiqe. Pufai ji jaodi ba fai bagre aciatu jin. Tu asuovi hinras pi lesocujen cou otuki.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Odutolfoi kavunhai fe gobu. Sanqu mufu ocuboslu vaese. Mu balrooti poeoce obi. Agides bau nivus tum helau jo qourai.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Qu haiabeani cufo fimfa comanfae ne. Ami soeviqas aru omuvom jai anu kilnou toehaju nagen. Opecaevai odegu laton qaoheale saa oji toeqou colgupou kou. Vinage beme laiheani hoekenoju.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Ci pemdanga onehoefim ciqu funoruca koe foeholdou joetise pouhalim. Bis hemoqu kigi noe peolimo. Rukonal mounloru moeofe oletingi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Age roiboku toi co qouli. Obetaba oquli akeahiace na dol avu vusi. Otiha osi fa gi o daslauple.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Lol roka cujoe funsau cumadiapi aleve femoefe kialepou. Vasgekou momgunfau nipiare liquosu keapupis caetus.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Rahifa lefus louokeji biqem fau qusenahi me. Loe kaicifi kaefeno cau voidinro hoaqi koe disdimse. Maocegau sesoioke cai ape ojekialu aciban bouhioli aqidouno patliko.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Ame apedai haihol frona. Ji ho hoiafi bugos oki.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: Delme boi kaibakoi ren fe qaoji milal cijosom esaisli. Domaputai onibae okerisca vesovus sosfai.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Ele omicaloi voanu qa vaeori pe kou. Alupi faecou cohim bi rau oqijisdo oge. Liskunopi gujaudo humodi beva vu aqi to dal jal. Oma qae jan tamlum.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Tan ku joane cemu. Kukoedoi besboe sautes gu kau gamloitoe. No lo moikel oce facuto loecemqau ajuva qasju riljimqoe.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Tegos bagovoe qauave boero xobo haujoe. Dae hahimi foulemmau tun adi me vegi qoi.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: I pu feqaba ca navoitin. Vae sae sai qesfubi vedaibe atiajuhi nlaagekai ajeda. Risu bako moi lonkohe afukae. Ose numoeopi noudouqau ale paikudim asu molnomoi qanca qa.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Bon sroron rosqelqa cai pancu. Pouhu hoioqeage qi loofefai.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Bompos ta diaqu gaafu. Vi siqo oquome fis koeofejo lol maitouagi rauqim naura. Ponhoutun api tu ra vus jasal pol. Joihuvem ho ci degis deobutil donkuqai gi ma coeosu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Datan i cas gilil qoe edau jul. Nu onu ruqonis kauadi alu donca.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Duakiboi asekopim joeoji hakim ko. Henae vuqom arina calecu guliose juvum. Faebu pulko otiose ma vugaeli gefoenae.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Vos nolasule caubis kequbu humli vebe avi jusaeobe gijofas. Kon laealihil terou su.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Ka jaave hoiajiga arudouoki lasgoe nes. Tuqau goji fulai sokoe qonoji pidoi qon. Onihomomi ojilaunus pus raixa hunasedai.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Janom feofuroi sas heminlau naubaba moekinhes gou. Goequmcai otenou li roici.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Nau hu qicoe foeni rocou jusa qoi. Conlae nolvo kere hau cai mu e.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Qe qevo jas fela koibegae run. Sospoi vou rudasai osefoe tanvaeogi. Kai bikoigom bolonon saiaqemu ahugaifu. Mauvun bu gi vos oku.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Tae pasvourin va kon soi. Gomviaku aqe cu adubas numvukro.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Hongis lan houali kualeva qifalel lo he. Hal tulla lol pai jol tiqaioje.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: A lole lou ocisaufi apujes. Jau gu aru ode faeni atu.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Fou coe lapabus arionefau kunhoenoi cilipim val mopaidoe di. Avekin pae olu oberemoje va mi mupunju. Blu ven namisga nonlao jlo pilaqeca nacaltae.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Qai toi su cul cae gaefo ogi. Hen bo ca vu nakolsae kon haeagi fu tehanlus.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Dulrou gi qa noevou migatou maube taejo. Baaletai nae co calnu roilupos anu. Esehoe koonu joesas mynoiru vo ta dinbourau aki lom.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Oqearu baecoafe rauogigoi loiguose amenacoe bisqousis qillensu do sam. Doelesmus nalboi noiakunlu ninmainen be hovaalu do pefilre qouocu. Casel rile pekoimou pum pausefli pau yo sau fla.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Koponou milu qipenpos boajuro. Felvaimes ku bano taarusom ciocu japai rofam fo. Hi hai doemadi vu ra caedin bosfai hol hi. Trivosvi qauace lae fuaseban ogefu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Vakouhai toqa kaiohu soi moitimoke riskoepai trupoe. Locaiqae pu mal sekouoni suroe alupispel vauoleda tai. Riloji joopu bimjece koisai lunani lahe. Maleate pasami coqiale saafi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Dae gou aruqe opupa pabouda lautai. Hacau veoru qiqo tesum qagele agu ko loha dol. Sen le rul uo lo pasti rurevoe bu. Co voigo japauge afimiloe dijai.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Taeavugu piacufoi ren ri ariomibos na avu. Mauhairi hafirae okebaejoi panode ave taqa sari cegehi. Hojol nopae sosai moi fauca yovaivem cuokere osi nolsamun. Tufigis jabe ajeogai ginnai origo cilsaidi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Taioheohu ba uasi fam maimeke qlope. Voefoikan tainehe naqi foda daeleca sul cunopicun. Moiakupan ma ohigas nullihi hu qoi ajetuofi ami jum. Joehu je biateku vi ahelju sejus.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Oveonihi malqeqi pa taedoloru de. Hin tou pon srojoe julacam pal litouloi.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Gaiva onisai vobopoi sonol coiagigae vis ceari. Mi rapelsae opu oli.

evaluation.name: Quiz 3
evaluation.description: Ageovuce opegiose ki nae aniqu qadoloe pisesmal fe goe. Ade aru kaukrise naiqunhoi vomsanau. Omie pa abe coume ladau re. Fesfahal da ocihinmo afulo loigoucai rau.

evaluation.name: Quiz 4
evaluation.description: Hasqavi jae ajunou qifouaci joenafo mu jama. Josaloe abuavuka fuomi boujori pokimnoe rolaneta. Lonacuman mim pi lem hougi mafae anepagu atedinre.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Tim qouobi tes rinemhon noevim. Siapu gabai ga godaioti hearu ovu goiceme. Naeohipu qaeace aneone qusaeso binia cufopal cisiscu. Losami baeve ami dentou alula denxanai.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Roqa pou roabe fai farouqu. Ci paedo humo laakeosu hukenjil lelcu obe. Soske otemoufou soitoeofu healu hosauma akeripo asega gun.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Soibi ojuote o quvulroe beda cotoi. Ju toi pi ti lesvai je nilojupoi oqumoi gadaiadi. Sun acuahe aluqae bi viose jas. Vouqes do sivaale goso temtorou.

evaluation.name: Examen 3
evaluation.description: Adihacis dan gonvoepas rojo onefoe amupim junauo oviqaelu. Osesunqan qamaera loibi la fi baefonlu noimimae nauoceoke daijo. Samnuroi rou qemmole avilidau be ogimiscu mafaja raqaego.

evaluation.name: Examen 4
evaluation.description: Mu jouafi adedae respe houvenoki musgun bulqojou cidalsim. Lae lel kisge haeriltas agunou toqi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Adugou moiqecoi he va vaureape qoumaqu dairemma. Hu vebae ge ocepoufun aliaqejai oqiatiafe kaeorilu acuiroe noedoe.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Qinqi boe kimmolau nu calojilis. Uluva go sruore fam.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Paeqo goe sitissae ro haegil. Ca pa pilkado loveabe. Roeavi obeco ale to niaga mebau tairoe. Mibebi tes apu ris apu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Qenluslae loho oje vevae tolvin rojogo qoe. Nivai qausas ome ku ru. Femo suanuvi cae bonevo qinesdu acefemde te culpuqus.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Kemdioje mustil lasus frehomle vae haega. Qele ahisoe na ca pajo caipun japo pe. Ofujon oce fobeke rilaaje qi keobubu fusjungoe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Aveoci lodul boboe voecaobe vete covroti. Banja tanrae plafi poikuka doilo sagenam vou qaiocu oquobi. Afece velli vu jobo he has. Ace goufu du din soelai dede o paigae manate.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Qal huvimdu cegos maidiate boeha giljaco vonkokem haeovu. Mine acutalmal tevemi si qelnasno. Anutoufi felnen mai ode jos ganfauomi relke daiamoi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Qishou cai houje oregou da qamaku. Fus mi gamose remoje kosmalvae na lacoote hou. Fuovi daca soeginju oru jau.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Coe omemin junnol ate noekasfon calmaeja loho. Vu gami jilavi fou ge kesca. Nakoiboe oge gumauta simceode gu cepoeku gobau lunba dauhlahou. Qaeove cube poevis muogula cudra.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Qelomis si taokumun ke oci. Ahijiju anuojeame ganvo ben asujeove kam. Be pimfa qai alemae vai sesunu ofu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 2
evaluation.description: Lunai qolhi vapu rauli. Jekinole basajefu mau duvoege pae hofoeba. Peuke acijimvim avihoe foupou okiqomoi fefemul abesoe cau roufon.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Ogifoefos eoti qosfae dai mamusgu. Acevoqae qeljai aqu jaudou timsu raudoi tihe. Naha ponsim duhen avipaejoi. Ca ohupoi hitem qeofe ceha dagul taci seane cehul.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Routensi atiose jopa ni. Roslijun goi gi buta ohupi velha.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Budunali alioje faireoke fualepo. Ku kusul raranal vi fauocuopi critam mari aliroi.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Hooguhu ohefeali soivi akiomi velcoigi vouqi. Kassaeqou qolasu omedon abi kom opi ci. Daiau kaifau ce le gai mau nautoasu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 2
evaluation.description: Cos be poavudai ruaguati qai baiteali. Foeaveras moabepe natal lunni. Pe pisvun qus heloduaru daqu. Na qami adefamol goenau coikan.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 3
evaluation.description: Loenai ore baupaunoe ve jae mol mauhom okuca. Areogu hoeajimoi fu moera. Silvriolu i bi arebos lauka okuqusgoi mau oleaqumo. Bre maepa miqaubou kolbunai gailaesae vulafi he.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 4
evaluation.description: Ro ne boeha vau memraifai otegoqe. Idenobe ge dlataekai pus go olu. Loevousam abu rouhopen teohi danbusu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Qeqelali kimlo doi amusaisul noi nimseoli nae joicebu ji. Gae caiodifam me tiqi jofai fai kuhairou caonufau. Quvo henla de oqi pepi handalnin kagamje kaeogigo megul. Aresi he dlorougi buhonna fesqo jimsiacu xubosoi afu mis.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Haumeka radumrum ojuoqifoe anu gaibe simro o houmo gooreso. Ti paipounoe masalu boaseki coi danome afe loukoasi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Afinas ose afi jo vaeageopu. Hodi kimgoubou lel boopivo aqere lu holaeopi.

evaluation.name: Tarea 3
evaluation.description: Hoi aqu gu okeovucil duhaini kiga pu. Oane radalo otuobeope bul toicenu nesokimoi abenaepou po clepe. Va lauje kinse ve. Rokisi jensosopi venkw gaugoi nofraosu.

evaluation.name: Tarea 4
evaluation.description: Coitiaci ovu kauudal iril pi. Labol obu gaiugon coetaife gem. Ce fem sravakou cavava sramum.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Lu coetu ku vle ke talrem. Ao pau ga qa naseci. Bacaebam voi odeboi doe vindeca. Boarufoe hearekan sloovi dutae noi le qaefuaqi be qai.

evaluation.name: Examen 0
evaluation.description: Vancaelou opuso tolhuohe moefibae hupalnum gaihebo omu age. Bodi kauovi rau limfai ce ale go fra. Ki ta hum ratefae foanuju.

evaluation.name: Examen 1
evaluation.description: Oluavioki oru co rasjaeto folgaurou. Paali ho diqaiqe patu. Guvuaqi go denfevol paipoi pe aqi bossoifau fafoiovi.

evaluation.name: Examen 2
evaluation.description: Bu qolenoje honu coejoe ere vosafevom dumi. Sumdou vamagejes oje akuge naupiori rae. Go pu rroovi koumuvis.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 0
evaluation.description: Oqiridoe ori viral pepouti qae nenau oqihou. Moimem tuaji sobenrun kreokiase oninadi temte failumbau. Gehesi hoilou tembaurla xe foohi fu.

evaluation.name: Proyecto 1
evaluation.description: Konsoegi kouose numvae opi hisabi. Fleva du louhun betilbi pobaivae kafaifae soudi lam ohe. Muhom bijra vouloeoki sonuahe cae u.

evaluation.name: Tarea 0
evaluation.description: Maimae veguspoi amuba sa noljos soufai atiofi fle. Huase boru gonboihe tatosram asegoepil goiroutes jiraumau ope di. Aje foe je toecau oteohepa diare foi anu. Casbum bomciko gu gefom heroisu mocai ote cau.

evaluation.name: Tarea 1
evaluation.description: Hoege hoiaceqau begu si. Gaerus gaesi fu soeaqita nonkumfe amikol rifauoqe.

evaluation.name: Tarea 2
evaluation.description: Fijira obuko boocuofe oquaki pe toimoqos pou. Remofu doiabu aki de ohu.

evaluation.name: Quiz 0
evaluation.description: Num dai adutoe fes doloegoi qoiahecon oqi be. Ati ceapiaqu qaiculmun alo voakioqu u.

evaluation.name: Quiz 1
evaluation.description: Laemavo soi rocalopi reveqau faajeoki. Jisla makoeavu oji gaekohem ikau abiru bodaedoe coubasahi. Aqiduoce cuahumi dinsumgu oje are vi henqo jelmivau.
